# AeroCraft Portal Code Style

## Component Rules
- One component per `.tsx` file ‚Äî no exceptions
- No inline styles ‚Äî use Bear `bearStyled`, Provider, or Tailwind classes only
- No magic numbers ‚Äî extract to `numbers.const.ts`
- No hardcoded strings ‚Äî all UI text must go through i18n (`useI18n()`)

## File Responsibilities
- `*.types.ts` ‚Äî interfaces and type aliases only
- `*.const.ts` ‚Äî constants, numbers, strings
- `*.tsx` ‚Äî single React component

## Imports
- `import type` for all type-only imports
- Path aliases: `@/*`, `@types/*`, `@const/*`, `@i18n/*`, `@pages/*`, `@components/*`
- No `../../` relative paths when an alias is available

## Bear Components Only
- Use Bear for all UI: `Card`, `Typography`, `Button`, `Flex`, `Badge`, `Divider`, `Input`, `Tabs`, `AppBar`, `Sidebar`, `Dropdown`, `Chip`, `Alert`, `Spinner`
- Colors via `BearProvider` theme ‚Äî never hardcode color values inline
- No raw `<div>` for layout ‚Äî use `<Flex>` or `<Card>`
